    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/350c2fc03bd5b992656d127263870682.avif?t=1713367768\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>环游世界，从北美洲的皑皑雪山到非洲一望无垠的撒哈拉沙漠，踏遍世界的每个角落！探访名胜古迹，感受历史人文，建立贸易路线，采购当地特色商品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/5a134a1f03d4f7610b5a39e359bb5e86.poster.avif?t=1713367768\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/5a134a1f03d4f7610b5a39e359bb5e86.webm?t=1713367768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/5a134a1f03d4f7610b5a39e359bb5e86.mp4?t=1713367768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/5fe6ee1469e67c5236ac54651b3b683b.avif?t=1713367768\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>踏上旅途，收获精良装备武装船队！配置你的刀枪炮甲，直面海盗与神秘生物的挑战与威胁。别忘了灵活运用战斗手册， &quot;剪刀石头布&quot;可是胜利第一要义。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/c6da0f310b05a8506f65ab783a177a87.poster.avif?t=1713367768\" width=598 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/c6da0f310b05a8506f65ab783a177a87.webm?t=1713367768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/c6da0f310b05a8506f65ab783a177a87.mp4?t=1713367768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/d0a90f5d2f6831c5446061bbf88ec7e7.avif?t=1713367768\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>平衡船内布局，关注船只状态，顺利的航行可不能忽视细节！装备大炮，船队在战斗中将所向披靡；设置船舱，船员在航行中将斗志昂扬；安设货舱，每次旅途都将收获满满。定制心仪船只，寻找更多可能！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/4aba14b90b9c980625ce9ce737a99525.poster.avif?t=1713367768\" width=598 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/4aba14b90b9c980625ce9ce737a99525.webm?t=1713367768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/4aba14b90b9c980625ce9ce737a99525.mp4?t=1713367768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/ebf571e034db567850078762fefb2094.avif?t=1713367768\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>成为世上最伟大的探险家！接取公会委托，探索各地奇观，找到未知宝藏，提升船队声望，在通往巅峰的旅途中获得皇室青睐，开启新的篇章！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/0340132239a9cb2a8d8c0c30c318a285.poster.avif?t=1713367768\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/0340132239a9cb2a8d8c0c30c318a285.webm?t=1713367768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120310/extras/0340132239a9cb2a8d8c0c30c318a285.mp4?t=1713367768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
